title: Get it NOW! Updated Features, Vaulted Ceiling, Outstanding Views!
posting_body: ['Property Listing# 019', 'This apartment features upgraded appliances, granite countertops, wood plank flooring, second floor, wooded view, 2 walk-n closets, GREAT VIEW!', 'Vaulted ceilings!', 'This beautiful community is located in Northwest Austin, with close proximity to the Technology Corridor, Central Business District, the Arboretum retail district, and the University of Texas!', 'Set in a striking hillside location on scenic Cat Mountain, residents enjoy an impressive array of community amenities, including the swimming and volleyball pools surrounded by lush landscaping.', 'Apartment Features', 'One- and two-bedroom apartments', 'Two-bedroom townhomes with garages', 'Nine-foot ceilings and cathedral ceilings', 'Wood-burning fireplaces with tile hearths and surrounds', 'Full-size washer/dryer connections', 'Built-in bookshelves', 'Decks and patios', 'Community Amenities', 'Hillside setting with views of Cat Mountain', 'Tiered swimming and volleyball pools, cantilevered over a wooded hillside', 'Native, xeriscape landscaping', 'Convenient to Downtown, the University of Texas, the Arboretum, and the Highland and Lakeline Malls', 'Do not miss this!', 'Call today to schedule your showing!', 'show contact info', 'licensed agent', 'Matt Davidson ~over 28 years of leasing experience in Austin~', 'Dash Realty', 'Dash Apartment Locating', 'Property Listing# 019', 'I have access to over 1000 listings, and can help you with all your renting needs!', 'FREE SERVICE TO YOU, NO FEES!']
